flowchart TD
    A[New Feature or Architectural Change] --> B{Processes sensitive or personal data?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Apply LINDDUN]
    B -->|No| D[Apply STRIDE]

    C --> E{Has trust boundary changes?}
    D --> E

    E -->|Yes| F[Update DFD and Abuse Stories]
    E -->|No| G[Reuse Existing Threat Model]

    F --> H[Define Security and Privacy Requirements]
    G --> H
    H --> I[Implement Controls and Add Pipeline Gates]
